id: pm-6irg
title: validate lifecycle cycle detection treats non-directional related edges as ordering edges (reciprocal related links flag a false-positive dependency cycle)
description: Restrict lifecycle cycle detection to directional ordering edges so reciprocal related links do not produce false-positive dependency cycles.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[2]: governance,validate
