author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: Reciprocal related links between two items produce zero lifecycle dependency-cycle warnings; a true blocked_by cycle still warns; a related edge opposing a blocked_by edge does not count as a cycle; regression test covers the related-only and mixed pairs
parent: pm-33cw
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Lifecycle dependency-cycle detection now traverses ordering relationship kinds only.
expected_result: Related edges never create cycle warnings; blocked_by cycles still do.
actual_result: Registry-driven validation excludes associative edges and retains ordering cycles.
